entries.femaleVariant: Ehhh... Everyone's a sellout these days. All these great artists, falling one by one.
If someone told my mother fifty years ago that Eurodyne'd sell out too... Pff.
If you're a rebel, you die for what you believe in...
Or you live long enough to join the system and fade away. No other option.
Well said, choom. Another decade or two, nobody'll even remember the guy.
They'll find another kid with big dreams, promise him a mountain of ganic gold... then muzzle him with a corpo contract.
Shit, man... We believed in you, Kerry.
